          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>School Security and Facilities Enhancement to Yield Results Act of 2018 or the School SAFETY Results Act of 2018 </b></p> <p>This bill amends the Internal Revenue Code to exclude from gross income a portion of the law enforcement pension received by a retired law enforcement officer who is volunteering as a school resource officer at an elementary or secondary school. </p> <p>The amount of the exclusion per year may not exceed the lesser of: (1) the product of $10, multiplied by the number of hours the individual spends performing school resource service during the year; and (2) $2,000.</p>]]></text>
          <updateDate>2018-09-28T04:00:00Z</updateDate>
          <name>Introduced in House</name>
